---
title: Baked Greek Style Cheese with tomatoes, cucumber and bulgur
description: Baked cheese can never be a bad thing, and the herby, warm, creamy Greek style cheese in this recipe certainly proves this point. Roasted veg, crunchy cucumber and fluffy bulgur further add to this sublime salad.
